      "message": "that\u0027s probably not what we want to do here. A better solution would be to:\n\n- Provide a utility function to convert from Windows 16-bit wchar_t to a String containing the equivalent UTF-8 text.\n\n- Ensure the implementation of runCommand() takes UTF-8 strings as input, and calls CreateProcessW() explicitly (instead of CreateProcess() which will translate to CreateProcessA() by default), converting the input to wchar_t strings as expected.\n\nThis probably belongs to a different CL, I\u0027ll provide one.",
